<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Table Assignment Confirmed</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1625 0%, #2d1b3d 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .success-icon {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .assignment-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
        }

        .assignment-box h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .assignment-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .detail-item {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .detail-value {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .info-section {
            background: #f8f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .info-section h3 {
            color: #7c3aed;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚úÖ Check-In Complete!</h1>
            <p>Your table has been assigned</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="success-icon">üéØ</div>

            <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px;">Welcome, <%= teamName %>!</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 30px;">You have successfully completed Step 1
                of check-in.</p>

            <div class="assignment-box">
                <h2>Your Assignment</h2>
                <div class="assignment-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Table Number</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">
                            <%= tableNumber %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Room Number</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">
                            <%= roomNumber %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>üìç Next Steps</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Proceed to <strong>Room <%= roomNumber %></strong></li>
                    <li>Find <strong>Table <%= tableNumber %></strong></li>
                    <li>Complete Step 2 by scanning the QR code at your table</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important: Complete Step 2</h3>
                <p>You must complete the second check-in step by scanning the QR code present at your table. Click the
                    button below to open the scanner:</p>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="<%= checkin2Link %>" class="button">Complete Step 2 Check-In</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>üí° Tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Set up your workspace at the assigned table</li>
                    <li>Introduce yourself to neighboring teams</li>
                    <li>Note the locations of restrooms and refreshments</li>
                    <li>Keep track of judging schedules</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best of luck with your project!</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>